{"tid":1965372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國安威脅】美國批准Google連接美台海底光纖 條件是不准連接香港","createTime":"2020-04-09T12:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T21:34:22.000Z","uid":125168,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d78e24cf52a35882cf96006c5ba8c5b9b3c3ae40","tid":1965372,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"【國安威脅】美國批准Google連接美台海底光纖 條件是不准連接香港<br />\n蘋果：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JOLtEz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JOLtEz&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6a2cb5f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JOLtEz</a><br />\n<br />\n報道指，隨着中國對香港影響日益加大，早前國家電訊安全審查小組已關注香港自治正在惡化，美國監管部門開始考慮除本港以外的區內國家增加聯繫，但指出，電纜運營商同意保障措施便不會遭到美國安全機構反對擬建中的海底電纜。Google發言人指歡迎決定，形容計劃獲批對公司提供服務很重要。<br />\n<br />\n該電纜由美國Google、Facebook及中國鵬博士電信傳媒集團合資興建，全長8,000英里，造價達三億美元，為Google及Facebook提供更快的互聯網連線服務，應付亞洲市場業務。<br />\n<br />\n現時全球有約有300條海底光纖電纜，負責傳輸全球99%的數據，是網絡的重要基礎，但美國監管機構憂慮中國操控網絡傳輸，以及有潛在的間諜活動。"},{"pid":"d872a1776e7c27abd1d101a30fd02c043b7f4551","tid":1965372,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"其實起好未？"},{"pid":"35493e04cfaf72e2bc280e133f420bb4563b2407","tid":1965372,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0550e5233494eb2906dea4167b8ce6c95b360a","tid":1965372,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"64d28e316f0e806feddf9d7e94c95b21a9b0ab3d","tid":1965372,"uid":48362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:11:06.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong no IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ac8c1e7668011e1e10a160daf52a70